{"id":312419,"type":4,"name":"Centipede","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/58/81/312419_jL0L9.jpg","summary":"Centipede是由雅达利于1981年在街机游戏平台出品的纵版射击游戏，游戏由Ed Logg和Dona Bailey设计开发，其中Dona Bailey是当时游戏产业中少有的女性游戏设计者。这款游戏也是继吃豆人之后收到女性玩家欢迎的投币式街机游戏之一。在游戏中玩家需要对抗蜈蚣、蝎子、蜘蛛、跳蚤，一局游戏要等玩家消灭掉纷纷落下的蜈蚣之后才算结束。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>蜈蚣</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/38616\">Atari</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/38616\">Atari</a>、<a href=\"/person/39174\">Atari Corporation</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PSV</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PSP</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS3</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox 360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Mac OS X</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>DC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>GBC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>GB</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Commodore VIC-20</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>TI-99/4A</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Intellivision</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>IBM PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Commodore 64</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>ColecoVision</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>BBC Micro</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Atari 400/800</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Atari 7800</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Atari 5200</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Atari 2600</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Apple II</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>街机</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Atari 2600</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ACT</li><li><span